## Simple

---



[Power Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/power_types/simple)

Does nothing.

Type ID: `origins:simple`



---

### üìù Note

This power type can be used by <u>__addon__</u> developers by creating a new `PowerTypeReference` to provide functionality.






---

### Examples

```json
{
    "type": "origins:simple"
}
```

This example will do nothing. However, it's still visible in the origin's power list GUI.
